1. Installed NVM (Node Version Manager) using:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed and reopened the terminal to reload NVM.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0 using:
   nvm install 20.16.0

4. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using:
   npm install sass@3.7.4
